nlp.diff
Class IntVector

java.lang.Object
  nlp.diff.IntVector

public class IntVector
extends java.lang.Object

A Vector of ints since there is no such thing as Vector<int>. 

 Typical use:
 IntVector iv = new IntVector();
 iv.add(0);
 for(int i=0;i<iv.length();i++)
 {
   int x=iv.get(i);
 }
